snippet.title: Amber Heard FORCED to Apologize to Johnny Depp To Not End Up in Prison
snippet.description:
Amber Heard FORCED to Apologize to Johnny Depp To Not End Up in Prison
The now-famous editorial authored by tabloid executive editor Dan Wooten and published in April 2018 under the headline Gone Potty was an instant smash. Wooten criticised JK Rowling's decision to keep Johnny in the film in his column, accusing the author of being blinded by his friendship with the actor. You can read Wooten's column here.
